ike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"點解香港人唔做運動都咁長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457a9ab35b11e3fed81952e16053c18bd5b2d7bb","tid":722781,"uid":10296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"日日做，每日30分鐘到<br />\n初初做為咗減肥<br />\n依家係為咗keep 住唔好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07216e04372966e389ba3aadd3b0478b686a3ec","tid":722781,"uid":191450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"最少5日<br />\n行夜山  HIIT 跆拳<br />\nrest day做yoga"},{"pid":"94ace463d234e3cc64f0d8d697099337a09e9d27","tid":722781,"uid":147264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"1星期1-2日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06015b81f68d8269cc3d5d0868d21cf0ad1f0ac","tid":722781,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"唔做"},{"pid":"b6e4542846a494c1f7cd7cd3f24207de32e45390","tid":722781,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"Everyday!!!!!"},{"pid":"1f3eea3689cef481bab980a2eb2ff46d0e14793d","tid":722781,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:19:58.000Z","msg":"4日<br />\n以前中學日日都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d76c231c6bf571038304bf4a47bce17284d0b86","tid":722781,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"一日打波三日gym"},{"pid":"b770409ca7d69a42285855e02a334e61cc453590","tid":722781,"uid":4528,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"一星期做 五至六日<br />\n星期日係家庭日 我會休息<br />\n<br />\n星期一三五 做阻力訓練<br />\n<br />\n星期二四 就踏單車 45分鐘至90分鐘<br />\n心跳率要維持130-140之間<br />\n<br />\n如果真係無做運動，就睇返手機自己步左幾多步，最少要有12500步，唔夠就早幾個站落車，行返屋企，返到去就沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n因為晚上想陪屋企人食飯同玩<br />\n每日六點爬起身 七點去到Gym房<br />\n做完運動 就去食個早餐 9點去返工<br />\n每一日都會自我感覺良好 <br />\n好似好有生活品質咁<br />\n<br />\n利申：普通打工仔"},{"pid":"79ba6263cad1cec0d191e4778750a47d42b3b1d0","tid":722781,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"高爾夫當唔當運動先？"},{"pid":"3830608f6b0ff1c848499d7d98179dc62f74f46a","tid":722781,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"2日跑步,1日詠春"},{"pid":"658d683adbaf3b50143168c6625dbdc7d73bf244","tid":722781,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"每日<br />\n電巠"},{"pid":"3bee3a1bb53602f49246cfa6899b1f30e10e3422","tid":722781,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"5/7 gym"},{"pid":"a58c87ae1a5d7853922a891ab016540ccf764324","tid":722781,"uid":50882,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"起身果下已經做左sit up 啦"},{"pid":"7777ac418704cc24429e06d579c99c8044670dd9","tid":722781,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78018ad554690ecbc10b61345b12974655ff084c","tid":722781,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58f908c97b909f8a20099aec55cf1b624fdba669","tid":722781,"uid":179814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:10:21.000Z","msg":"每日"},{"pid":"cba230d5d37f090b5603f9dbb5bbbb0018241224","tid":722781,"uid":58031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"身邊啲人大多都係督電話督走左幾個鐘<br />\n然後同我講佢冇時間做運動<br />\n<br />\n好多人都當運動係要特別計劃先做得<br />\n其實將運動當娛樂/消遣就好易keep住做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：一星期三~四日"},{"pid":"8a99c329764cb578fedd48f1f1d52c798404ea3c","tid":722781,"uid":84908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-